@description ReaMole: Soundmole Extension for REAPER
@version 0.0.35
@author zaibuyidao
@donation https://www.paypal.me/zaibuyidao
@provides
  [darwin64      ] ReaMole/reaper_soundmole-x86_64.dylib > reaper_soundmole-x86_64.dylib
